    <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
        <img src="/img/first.jpg" width="607" height="510" class="'d-block mx-lg-auto img-fluid" alt="Cooking blog" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
        <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold mb-3">Huge selection of delicious recipe ideas</h1>
        <p class="lead">
            This website Blog is created so that people can add recipes and share them with others, 
